<p><strong>Continuing Student Deferment</strong></p>
<p>A Continuing Student Deferment allows a student to miss one of their on-track semesters without having to reapply for admission. Each student is allowed only one Continuing Student Deferment throughout their time at BYU-Idaho. <a class="intLink" href="x18877.xml">Click here to learn more.</a></p>
<p><strong>LDS Missionary Deferment</strong></p>
<p>Are you planning to serve a mission? We are ready to help. Students leaving to serve an LDS Mission may hold their enrollment while they serve by completing the LDS Missionary Admission Deferment.&nbsp;<a class="intLink" href="x18876.xml">Click here to learn more.</a></p>
<p><strong>Medical Deferment</strong></p>
<p>The Medical Deferment is used to help students deal with medical issues that prevent attendance during an assigned semester.&nbsp;<a class="intLink" href="x18875.xml">Click here to learn more.</a></p>
<p><strong>Spouse of Intern Deferment<br /></strong><br />The Spouse of Intern Deferment is used to help students defer a semester when an internship of a spouse prevents attendance during an assigned semester. The deferment also provides the opportunity to receive an override for the next off-track semester to allow the spouse of the intern to not fall behind in their graduation plans. <a class="intLink" href="x18874.xml" title="Spouse of Intern Deferment Web Page">Click here</a> to learn more about the Spouse of Intern Deferment.</p>]]></IntroCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="CellGroup" label="Cells" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><numColumns type="enumeration" values="1 2 3 4 5" label="Select number of cell columns." readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">3</numColumns><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Cell" Name="CellList" label="Cell List" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower></xPower><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_BannerAd" Name="BannerAds" label="Rotating Ads (650x216px required)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="BannerAd" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="" Query="" Name="DeptEvents" label="Define Your Events Folder" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupSt